      <guid>https://blog.jverkamp.com/2020/06/21/fables-vol.-3-storybook-love/</guid>
      <description>&lt;figure class=&#34;cover-image&#34;&gt;
                &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;book&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;21329&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21329.fables-vol-3-storybook-love&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.jverkamp.com/embeds/books/fables-vol-3-storybook-love.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
